{"tid":1001560,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"《金融時報》MBA排行榜2019香港三大學齊挫邊間跌得最勁？","createTime":"2019-01-30T08:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T11:45:25.000Z","uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c62d8713663ea5942a2add25f1ab6fdda95d9940","tid":1001560,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:49:40.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》公布2019年工商管理碩士（MBA）全球排名，香港科技大學商學院、香港大學商學院及香港中文大學商學院的課程繼續躋身100強，惟最新排名均錄得跌幅。科大商學院繼續為位列香港之首，最新排名為第18名，較2018年跌4位。<br />\n<br />\n史丹福商學研究院則蟬聯全球榜首席位，畢業生平均年薪達228,074美元，相當於約178萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n根據最新排名，香港大學位列全球第41名，較去年大跌8位，畢業生平均年薪131,386美元，相當於約102萬港元。而中大商學院則排全球第57名，較去年大跌14位，畢業生平均年薪115,689元，相當於約90.8萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n全球五強方面，史丹福商學研究院繼續排榜首，畢業生平均年薪達228,074美元；緊隨其後為哈佛商學院、歐洲工商管理學院（INSEAD），兩校畢業生的平均年薪為205,486美元及179,661美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLjFcL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLjFcL5.jpg&h=53e721c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9bda07b0ccd2a2f5025cd044c8273e4e1853c4a","tid":1001560,"uid":200521,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:36:52.000Z","msg":"啲19排名就算數喇"},{"pid":"244ee9991f5516c3f2fcf2076a1a696766637bc4","tid":1001560,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:40:41.000Z","msg":"香港三大唔係含樹鯨？"},{"pid":"318250a41fc4a3e919700358441c96393364d8c1","tid":1001560,"uid":216709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"港大畢業生平均年薪131,386美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部連登仔"},{"pid":"4f27db6b7e73a59fb3d65af0edd892fb1c020cb4","tid":1001560,"uid":201890,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"冇吾城既排名榜都系d 19 排名榜"},{"pid":"da6a80ee0725438c84332dd78396a8ed62936e89","tid":1001560,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:43:15.000Z","msg":"吾含先係世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c7ed8d553883eab0f7580dea801911c68e27d4","tid":1001560,"uid":138707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da6a80ee0725438c84332dd78396a8ed62936e89","tid":1001560,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:43:15.000Z","msg":"吾含先係世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:45:25.000Z","msg":"HSU &gt; CU &gt; UST &gt; HKU &gt; ChinU &gt; All"}]}